---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="The philosophy behind Monovus. A singular focus on building technology that works — quietly, reliably, and at scale."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-electric-cyan font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">About</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Quiet precision.<br />Relentless execution.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          Monovus exists because too much technology is built for show and not enough
          is built to last. We took a different path.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy Section -->
  <section class="pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-obsidian-light border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
          <!-- Philosophy -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-2">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">The Monovus Philosophy</h2>
            <p class="text-electric-cyan font-mono text-sm mb-6">Singular focus. No noise.</p>

            <div class="space-y-4 text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                We believe the best technology disappears. It doesn't demand attention —
                it earns trust by working flawlessly in the background. Every system we
                build is measured by one standard: does it work at 3 AM with nobody watching?
              </p>
              <p>
                Our approach is rooted in deep technical expertise across cloud platforms,
                DevOps practices, AI integration, and systems architecture. We've seen what
                breaks at scale and what survives. That experience shapes everything we build.
              </p>
              <p>
                The name "Monovus" reflects a singular focus: delivering solutions that
                are practical, reliable, and built to last. No unnecessary complexity.
                No technology for technology's sake. Just systems that work.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Focus Areas -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-6">Core Expertise</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <p class="text-white/80 text-sm font-medium mb-1">Cloud & Infrastructure</p>
                <div class="w-full bg-white/10 rounded-full h-1.5">
                  <div class="bg-electric-cyan h-1.5 rounded-full" style="width: 95%"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-white/80 text-sm font-medium mb-1">DevOps & Automation</p>
                <div class="w-full bg-white/10 rounded-full h-1.5">
                  <div class="bg-electric-cyan h-1.5 rounded-full" style="width: 90%"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-white/80 text-sm font-medium mb-1">AI & Machine Learning</p>
                <div class="w-full bg-white/10 rounded-full h-1.5">
                  <div class="bg-electric-cyan h-1.5 rounded-full" style="width: 85%"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-white/80 text-sm font-medium mb-1">Security & Zero Trust</p>
                <div class="w-full bg-white/10 rounded-full h-1.5">
                  <div class="bg-electric-cyan h-1.5 rounded-full" style="width: 88%"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-white/80 text-sm font-medium mb-1">Monitoring & Observability</p>
                <div class="w-full bg-white/10 rounded-full h-1.5">
                  <div class="bg-electric-cyan h-1.5 rounded-full" style="width: 92%"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Technologies</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              {['Docker', 'Kubernetes', 'Terraform', 'Grafana', 'Cloudflare', 'AWS', 'Linux', 'Python', 'TypeScript', 'n8n'].map((tech) => (
                <span class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white/60 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
                  {tech}
                </span>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Approach -->
  <section class="pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Our Approach</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Too many businesses struggle with technology that's over-engineered,
            under-maintained, or simply the wrong fit. The industry often sells
            complexity when what's needed is clarity.
          </p>
          <p>
            We take a different approach. Every engagement starts with understanding the
            problem — not selling a solution. We bring the same rigor to a small automation
            project as we do to a full infrastructure overhaul, because the details matter
            at every scale.
          </p>
          <p>
            Monovus operates as a lean, focused entity. No layers of management, no
            junior consultants learning on your dime. When you work with us, you work
            directly with senior expertise.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="pb-20 sm:pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-12 text-center">Principles</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-electric-cyan/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-electric-cyan font-mono font-bold text-lg">01</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Pragmatic</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">
            The simplest solution that solves the problem. No gold-plating,
            no resume-driven development.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-electric-cyan/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-electric-cyan font-mono font-bold text-lg">02</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Transparent</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">
            Clear communication, honest timelines, no surprises. If something
            isn't working, you'll hear about it early.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-electric-cyan/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-electric-cyan font-mono font-bold text-lg">03</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Reliable</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">
            We build systems that work at 3 AM without anyone watching. That same
            reliability applies to how we operate.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
